snippet.title: Goblin and Coins II coming soon trailer (April 2023)
snippet.description: New trailer for the Steam store page, showing of some random levels and mechanics. The game is planned to release in April 2023. Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/694990/Goblin_and_Coins_II/
